Ruth: (Phew... It seems like there's no one here
except for Sister. Moreover, she's focused on her
prayers.)

Eril: "That over there is my private room... Would
you like to take a look?"
Ruth: (Is Eril in this room...? But it's locked.)
Ruth: "Eril, if you're there, answer me."

Eril: "Lord Ruth...? What do you need at this late
hour...?"
Ruth: (Her holy magic might be useful...)
Ruth: "Hey, I need your power, so come out."

Eril: "Yes, understood... If I can be of
assistance to Lord Ruth, I'd be glad to..."

Eril: "Is that so... If you need anything, please
call on me."
Ruth: "Hey, I need your power, so come out."

Eril: "Yes, understood... If I can be of
assistance to you, Ruth-sama, I'd be glad to..."
Ruth: "No, never mind. I don't need anything."

Eril: "Is that so... If you need anything, please
don't hesitate to ask."

Eril: "Lord Ruth, is there something wrong with my
room?"

Eril: "Hyah... Who is it? You can speak to me
without hesitation, even during prayers..."

Eril: "Uh-um, uh-um... Is this... the real
thing...!?"

Eril: "Ahh, Lord Ruth... from now on, I dedicate
my everything to you..."

Ruth: (Even a priestess falls like this once she's
corrupted.)

Ruth: "(...I took a risk to obtain it, but there's
no use for this thing at the moment.)"

eventually...)"
Ruth: "No, nothing in particular right now."

Ruth: "Hey, hey, now's our chance! This is no time
to be scared!"
